animeTitle: Hifuu Katsudou Kiroku: The Sealed Esoteric History
animeDescription: Based on Team Shanghai Alice's Touhou Project.History revolves around the many events in the lives of two students from the Outside World - Maribel Hearn and Renko Usami. They are the only members of the "Hifuu Club Activity Record" who are looking for those hidden worlds as Gensokyo, the Netherworld and the Moon.(Source: AniDB)
